WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:03.000
Learners begin with a question and gather around notes and a laptop.

00:03.000 --> 00:07.000
Guided practice turns the question into examples, checks, and feedback.

00:07.000 --> 00:15.000
The learning session moves from the first question into a patient AI companion.

00:15.000 --> 00:23.000
Practice, hints, quizzes, and active learning loops keep the learner thinking.

00:23.000 --> 00:31.000
The closing beat returns to public access, schools, and a more open way to learn.
